name: Fractal Audio Axe-Fx III
description: Fractal Audio Systems’ new flagship processor brings more power, features, and upgrades than ever before. The Axe-Fx III is the latest in a line of legends — the world’s most powerful all-in-one processor for guitar, bass, and other instruments. Featuring Fractal Audio's latest amp modeling technology, thousands of UltraRes™ speaker cab simulations, and industry-leading effects, the Axe-Fx III has more raw power and features than any guitar processor ever created.

name: Fractal Audio FM3
description: Now you can get Fractal Audio’s industry-leading amp and cab modeling, plus a suite of stompbox and studio effects, a powerful foot controller, 4×4 USB audio — and more — all in a compact, rugged, all-in-one, floor unit designed for the studio or stage.

name: Kemper Profiler Head
description: But what if you want to place the factory sound with your own favourite personal sounds? Before the appearance of the Kemper Profiling Amps there were basically not many alternatives: you could either drag (before the digital revolution) all of your equipment from place to place, or you could do your best to adapt the factory sounds of the modelling amp as much as possible to your own desires.

name: Kemper Profiler Stage
description: The Kemper Profiling technique allows the creation of a very precise sonic image (profile) of an existing amplifier configuration (including speaker and microphone pickup). Thanks to the many internal editing options, such as various ground effect emulations (up to 4 simultaneously), master effects, equalizers, gain, amp definition, power sagging, etc., you can then edit the created sound far beyond the capabilities of the original amplifier.
